[06/02/2018 13:42:14] <font color="#00ff00">¡Adelante!</font>
[06/02/2018 13:42:17] <font color="#ffff00">Dame.</font>
[06/02/2018 13:42:39] <font color="#0000ff">(Gritos de guerra)</font>
[06/02/2018 13:43:02] <font color="#0000ff">(Música western)</font>
